	   <tr><td colspan=2>We see there was a need for usto make a registered account.  It seems, Shrikke, that you have the arrogance possessed by all the Shadow Knights.  We were hoping for more from you, but alas, we see it will not be so.<br><br>Your experiences of youth are interesting, and while completely different than ours(being a female of the Brood of Kotiz is a rare thing), We find that you keep the prejudice of your caste.<br><br>First, you PRESUME to study our dark arts, and then you betray those teachings by becoming allies of the Shaman.  We warn you now, choose carefully who you side with, because the revolution within Cabilis will soon be at hand.  Even now, your weak guild and its allies fear to act against the mighty Brood of Kotiz, and only OUR merchants are free of the tyranny you allow the Haggle Barron to possess.<br>&nbsp;<br>Usula Wurmbane<br>Iksar Necromancer<br>Queen of Fear</td></tr>
