	   <tr><td colspan=2>Oh, mightest of the self proclaimed lords of the green, smelly, butt iching types...<br><br>It has been known for many seasons that the armies, lead by Innoruuk, have been gathering.  And do not fear, my fellow Iksars and I will be more than happy to stand still and wait for your (What did you call it?  Oh..yes.)  Your "Great Offensive(tm)" to come wandering into our lands.  Actually, we thank you for bringing our past slaves and servants back to us, instead of us having to extend our reach and dragging them back from the ill fated life they live in "Da Swamp".<br><br>Trolls don't make the best slaves but could be considered amusing in a "Look, that troll has his finger stuck in his nose" sort of way.  Plus, make excellent fertilizer when ground up properly.<br><br>Dragons, Giants, and our own creations have waged war to wipe the Iksar from the face of Norrath.  I'm assuming that a bunch of liquored up, green, pimply butted trolls will be more of an afternoon tea party, then a real war.<br><br>And if you want to know fear, I would suggest you consider what happened to your kind the last time your failed your god.  He turned you into the gelatenous blobs you are today.  And to add insult to injury, turned your woman into the third...behind female ogers and dwarfs...ugliest creatures on the planet.  No wonder your race is so hostile.<br><br>I welcome your kind to my continent of Kunark.  Please come over and pick up your maid uniform anytime you like.<br><br>With all due respect and in the tradition of the rant...<br><br>/ooc I'm assuming this is a fun bantering of words.  Pusbag, I have enjoyed your posts over the last year.  Please feel free to post here anytime you like.  Your particular sense of gaming is refreshing :-)<br>&nbsp;<br>Shrikke - Knight of Fear<br>Bristlebane</td></tr>
