	   <tr><td colspan=2>I to follow the path of fear. Tho the Hierophan did not see in me the spark of Cazic-Thul that would allow me to hear is voice as a crusader nor the wisdom that is needed whit the role of a scaled mystic, my physical strength was unrivaled by most other of my generation and so they sent me to Fortress Talishan opon my waking i was greeted by the leer of a drill master. My youth was spent listening to tales of the brothers defender of the chosens heros and yet betrayers of our kind, and of the epic battles of Karnor and Chardok. Opon rebirth i was given my first pike and sent to the Feild of bone's garisson. from there i hardened and i am now a full legionnair of cabilis. Tho i am now rarly near Cabilis or even on Kunark. i still follow the our ways and salut any Crusaders i encounter and kneel befor the Scaled mystics, and only the pact of order keeps me from killing any and all soft skin i meet and make their chilhood nightmare, reality.<br>&nbsp;<br>Daakar Sathir Trooper of Cabilis of 34 season.<br>"When other fall to spear and sword, we must stand."</td></tr>
